<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <title>Airbnb</title>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/style.scss">
    <script src="assets/style.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>

    <header class="header">
      <nav class="navbar fixed-top navbar-white bg-white navbar-style">
         <h1 class="text-danger font-weight-bold">Airbnb</h1>
          <ul class="nav justify-content-end">
          <li class="nav-item nav-item-style">
            <a class="nav-link active" href="#">ホストをはじめる</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item nav-item-style">
            <a class="nav-link" href="#">アカウント作成</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item nav-item-style">
            <%= link_to "ログイン", new_user_session_path %>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="row row-1">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <!-- <img class="d-block w-100" src="images/image1.jpeg" alt="First slide"> -->
            <%= image_tag 'image1.jpeg' %>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="images/image2.jpeg" alt="Second slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="images/image3.jpeg" alt="Third slide">
            </div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

      <div class="container container-style">
        <div class="row row-1">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h1>ユニークなお家を予約して暮らすような旅をしよう。</h1>
              <div class="input-group">
                <input type="text" name="serach" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="エリアを入力">
                <span class="input-group-btn">
                  <button class="btn btn-default btn-danger" type="submit">Search</button>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">お住いの国の宿泊先</h2>
        <div class="row row-2">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card" style="width: 20rem;">
              <img class="card-img-top" src="images/image0.jpeg" alt="Card image cap">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text font-weight-bold">宿泊先</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">ご興味のある宿泊先</h2>
        <div class="row row-2">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card" style="width: 20rem;">
              <img class="card-img-top" src="images/image0.jpeg" alt="Card image cap">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text font-weight-bold">宿泊先</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    <footer class="footer footer-style">
      <p class="text-center">@Airbnb_Team</p>
    </footer>

  </body>

</html>
